hands_on_practices.solution:
我们从现今单一中微子种类的费米-狄拉克动量分布开始，
$$dn(p)=\frac{g_\nu}{(2\pi\hbar)^3}\frac{4\pi p^2\,dp}{e^{p c/(k_B T_{\nu,0})}+1}\,. $$

1. 速度矩。在非相对论极限下 $v=p/m_\nu$，所以
$$\langle v^2\rangle=\frac{\int v^2\,dn}{\int dn}
=\frac{\int p^2/m_\nu^2\,dn}{\int dn}
=\frac{\langle p^2\rangle}{m_\nu^2}\,,$$
且一维弥散为
$$\sigma_v^2=\frac{1}{3}\langle v^2\rangle=\frac{1}{3}\frac{\langle p^2\rangle}{m_\nu^2}\,. $$

2. 计算 $\langle p^2\rangle$。定义 $x=p c/(k_B T_{\nu,0})$，则 $p=(k_B T_{\nu,0}/c)x$ 且 $dp=(k_B T_{\nu,0}/c)\,dx$。于是
$$\langle p^2\rangle
=\frac{\displaystyle\int_0^\infty p^4\frac{dp}{e^x+1}}
     {\displaystyle\int_0^\infty p^2\frac{dp}{e^x+1}}
=(\tfrac{k_BT_{\nu,0}}{c})^2
\frac{\displaystyle\int_0^\infty x^4/(e^x+1)\,dx}
     {\displaystyle\int_0^\infty x^2/(e^x+1)\,dx}\,. $$
使用
$$\int_0^\infty\frac{x^{s-1}}{e^x+1}dx=(1-2^{1-s})\Gamma(s)\zeta(s)\,, $$
我们得到
$$\int_0^\infty\frac{x^4}{e^x+1}dx=(1-2^{-4})\Gamma(5)\zeta(5)=\frac{15}{16}\cdot24\,\zeta(5)=\frac{45}{2}\zeta(5),$$
$$\int_0^\infty\frac{x^2}{e^x+1}dx=(1-2^{-2})\Gamma(3)\zeta(3)=\frac{3}{4}\cdot2\,\zeta(3)=\frac{3}{2}\zeta(3).$$
因此
$$\langle p^2\rangle=(\tfrac{k_BT_{\nu,0}}{c})^2\frac{\frac{45}{2}\zeta(5)}{\frac{3}{2}\zeta(3)}
=(\tfrac{k_BT_{\nu,0}}{c})^2\,15\frac{\zeta(5)}{\zeta(3)}\,. $$

3. 令 $\sigma_v=v_{esc}$。由于
$$\sigma_v^2=\frac{1}{3}\frac{\langle p^2\rangle}{m_\nu^2}
=\frac{1}{3}\frac{(k_BT_{\nu,0}/c)^2\,15\,\zeta(5)/\zeta(3)}{m_\nu^2}
=\frac{5\,\zeta(5)}{\zeta(3)}\frac{k_B^2T_{\nu,0}^2}{c^2\,m_\nu^2}\,, $$
设 $\sigma_v^2=v_{esc}^2$ 可得
$$m_\nu^2=\frac{5\,\zeta(5)}{\zeta(3)}\frac{k_B^2T_{\nu,0}^2}{c^2\,v_{esc}^2}
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
m_\nu=\frac{k_BT_{\nu,0}}{c\,v_{esc}}\sqrt{\frac{5\,\zeta(5)}{\zeta(3)}}\,. $$
